# Runbook Protocol

Before non-trivial work, read targeted sections from `.cursor/runbook/` (start at `00_INDEX.md`). Do not load all files at once.

| Task type | Read |
|-----------|------|
| New feature / refactor | `01_ARCHITECTURE.md` + `02_COMPONENTS_AND_FILES.md` |
| Bug fix | `04_CURRENT_STATE.md` + relevant component doc |
| Style / conventions | `03_RULES_AND_STANDARDS.md` |

Before committing, update runbook files if stack, structure, standards, or project status changed. Ground claims in actual code.
